<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM9.1">
<l>cinturac cempoṭip pōltiru māliruñ cōlaiyeṅkum</l>
<l>intira kōpaṅka ḷēyeḻun tumparan tiṭṭaṉavāl</l>
<l>mantara nāṭṭiyaṉ ṟumatu rakkoḻuñ cāṟukoṇṭa</l>
<l>cuntarat tōḷuṭai yāṉcuḻa laiyiṉiṉ ṟuytuṅkolō.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Cochineals have risen and spread everywhere</l>
<l>in Tirumāliruñcōlai like the red dust of vermilion. Alas!</l>
<l>Will we escape from the deception of Him with beautiful shoulders</l>
<l>who obtained the sweet, luxurious essence,</l>
<l rend="indent">having set up the Mandara [mountain as a churning staff] that day!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
